</li_value>                   <p base="F55752519" id="IFRS17_P2228" class="- topic/p ">Insurance finance expenses are the same as in <xref href="IFRS17_gIE18-IE23.dita#IFRS17_gIE18_IE23/IFRS17_gIE18_IE23_TI" base="F59533929" id="IFRS17_X1035" class="- topic/xref ">Example 2A</xref>. The whole amount of insurance finance expenses is related to the liability for remaining coverage because the liability for incurred claims is paid immediately after the expenses are incurred.</p>                 </li></ol>             </entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></body></paragraph>